{"tid":2200785,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳大陸武裝漁船包圍東沙島  台政府否認","createTime":"2020-09-13T09:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T09:02:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15ace895daf12f7fe5e183156d1bd45977ba22ad","tid":2200785,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T09:02:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200913/I7WUT7W5FNF2LONK6257CO7WSM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200913%2FI7WUT7W5FNF2LONK6257CO7WSM%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Qx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=9eaef732\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200913%2FI7WUT7W5FNF2LONK6257CO7WSM%2F&h=72d5de6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200913/I7WUT7W5FNF2LONK6257CO7WSM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n傳大陸武裝漁船包圍東沙島  台政府否認<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IkCgd5eGOJhg5E03EMNRVQOdn6A=/1438x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SJ4V6RBVPVHFXJNKKN7AA3QCOQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIkCgd5eGOJhg5E03EMNRVQOdn6A%3D%2F1438x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSJ4V6RBVPVHFXJNKKN7AA3QCOQ.jpg&h=19f521bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大陸海上民兵隊被視為非正規海軍部隊。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】台灣立委王定宇透露，東沙島正被大陸武裝漁船隊包圍，又指以往解放軍使用的圍點阻援做法，多半用在南海其他國家，首次針對台灣外島較罕見。然而，海巡署昨急緊回應，只有貨輪無害航行通過，沒有包圍情況。雖然包圍東沙島消息充滿疑雲，但可以肯定的是，解放軍戰機繞台飛行、海上大型軍事演習，一直沒有停止過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fe3icheHmtV9NlwwID8Efybh0yw=/780x768/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VYYBCEX5JVCJHGG7Q7GTCVUJFU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFe3icheHmtV9NlwwID8Efybh0yw%3D%2F780x768%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVYYBCEX5JVCJHGG7Q7GTCVUJFU.jpg&h=7c85a472&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中共出手將因小失大<br />\n<br />\n民進黨立委王定宇前日在電視節目提到，東沙島上周三（9日）起疑遭中國海上民兵、船隻包圍，在AIS自動船舶識別系統發現，東沙島四周是紅點，行動至前日已超過60小時，還在持續進行。海巡署昨回應，報道非事實，當時有六艘商貨輪航行通過，東沙島未被包圍。不過，大陸武裝漁船隊並非罕見，美國海軍戰爭學院分析，..............................<br />\n<br />\n台灣戰略學會研究員蘇紫雲向本報表示，台灣離島易攻難守，...........................<br />\n<br />\n此外，江蘇連雲港海事局昨刊登公告，今至20日於黃海南部範圍展開軍事演習，.................."}]}